stylometry: Data mining involves searching data for information that is useful to a company.  We used data mining in our cluster analysis.  First, we must gather data and organize it in a workable fashion.  Then we standardize the data.  This avoids some of the issues we might encounter if we used absolute numbers.  Expressing individual datum as a relation to the rest of the data allows us to make comparisons and calculations that otherwise would be very complex.  Data mining is important in business because it can give a company insight into who their customers are, where they live, where they shop, and their spending habits.
